korean: 매일 아침 먹으려고 책상 위에 놓아뒀어.
효과가 있는지는 잘 모르겠지만 안심은 된다.
꾸준히 먹는 게 중요하다는데 잊지 말아야지.
english: I've been tired lately, so I started taking multivitamins.
I put them on my desk to remember to take them every morning.
I'm not sure if they're working, but they give me peace of mind.
They say consistency is important, so I shouldn't forget.
